## Author Statement

**This software is dedicated to:**
- Open scientific knowledge
- Worker liberation
- The abolition of capitalist exploitation
- The commons of human intellectual labor

**The author, Lino P. Casu, explicitly rejects:**
- The commodification of software
- The extraction of surplus value from workers
- The enclosure of the intellectual commons
- The profit motive in scientific research

---

## DISCLAIMER

This software is a mathematical research framework for studying the theoretical
foundations of continuous worldline transfer within the Segmented Spacetime (SSZ)
framework. It does not claim that human teleportation is currently possible, nor
does it provide a blueprint for any device. The author explicitly forbids
biological system experiments until all prior experimental levels are validated
and appropriate ethics/legal review exists.

